_sText:
I did a dystopian version of my city and this is the result! Just mapping for art, so, don't expect much gameplay like a Dust map. It's more like a City 17 square. I took a lot of Half-Life 2 Beta content, like the AirExchange skybox, sounds and textures.

Hope you enjoy it!
